<p>Sell by adding products to the cart</p>

<p><strong>Follow the steps below:</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>Scan the product barcode (make sure the arrow in the computer is at the center of the screen)&nbsp;<strong>OR</strong></li>
	<li>For items without a barcode, type the product name/s on the search bar and add to the cart</li>
	<li>To add more products, either click on the ‘+’ sign or click in the box and type the number of products purchased</li>
	<li>To remove a product from the cart, click ‘x’ at the end of the product row or clear the entire cart by clicking the bin icon next to the sub total</li>
	<li>Select your mode of payment at the RetailPay POS checkout</li>
